data.description: Pastoral Privacy!  Tucked away in a peaceful setting is this unique home on 10 acres.  Space and sunshine abound while you enjoy casual life in the country. Incredible property with an opportunity to build a second home for your family.  The existing home features two bedrooms, one full bath, a living area and a kitchen upstairs. Downstairs you'll find a huge family room, a half bath, and a bonus room that is currently used as another bedroom.  There is a  separate room off of the family room that is perfect for additional storage or a workshop.  Listen to the quiet - this is a place to hang your heart!
